<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-KyZXEAg3QhqLMpG8r+8fhAXLRk2vvoC2f3B09zVXn8CA5QIVfZOJ3BCsw2P0p/We"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
      <header class="mb-auto">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
          <h3 class="float-md-left mb-0">QA_inIT</h3>
          <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-right">
            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
            <% if(!currentUser) { %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
            <% } else { %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/questions/new">New Question</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
            <% } %>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="px-3">
        <video class="video-container" muted autoplay loop>
          <source src="../qa.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </main>

<div class="container-fluid mt-5">
        <div class="row mt-3 mb-5">
          <div class="col-md-10 offset-1 mb-5">
             <h1>QA_inIT</h1>
            <p class="lead fs-5">
             Deare Friends. This Web App was developed specially for AQ automation. 
I was happy to work on this application for you, I believe our community will be stronger ,If we will be treating each other with support and kindness.
So let’s start from support and knowledge sharing<br>
How to use?  Well its simple, just register and enjoy all functionality, If you are just a visiting… well then observe our questions and feedbacks we are giving to each other. <br> And remember educating others it means create I peaceful work environment for yourself. 
            </p>
              <button class="switch-btn">
        <span>play</span>
        <span>pause</span>
        <span class="switch"></span>
      </button>
    </header>
          </div>

        </div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-6">
         <div class="card shadow">
      <div class="card-body">
 <h5 class="lead text-secondary"> any offers</h5>, 
 <p class="text-dark">You can contact me at any time through the contact form or by email: <strong>liubovtrudovaapplying@gmail.com </strong></p>
 <p class="text-dark">Also, this application clearly has some problems. there is some I know about, and some I have no idea of their existence, feel free to point it out, and i'll be fixing them on the flight!</p>
 </div>
 </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-6">
 
           <div class="card shadow">
       <%- include("./layouts/partials/flash.ejs") %>
      <div class="card-body">
       
        <h5 class="lead text-dark">please leave your contact information below, and I'll reach out to you as soon as posible</h5>
        <form
          action="/"
          method="post"
          class="validated-form"
          novalidate
        >
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="fullname" class="form-label text-dark">Full Name</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              name="fullname"
              id="fullname"
              placeholder="Full Name"
              required
            />
            <div class="valid-feedback">Looks good</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label text-dark">Email</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              class="form-control "
              name="email"
              id="email"
              placeholder="email"
              required
            />
            <div class="valid-feedback">Looks good</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="phone" class="form-label text-dark">Phone number</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              name="phone"
              id="phone"
              placeholder="Phone number"

            />
            <div class="valid-feedback">Looks good</div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <button class="btn btn-dark">Get in touch</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>



  </div>
</div>
        </div>
      <footer class="mt-autho py-3 footer text-white">
        <p>&copy; Liubov Trudova <%= new Date().getFullYear()%></p>
      </footer>
    </div>
